      "rationale": "Material properties (elastic modulus, yield strength, tangent modulus) were derived from tensile coupon tests performed on material from the same lot as the test constructs. Geometric dimensions were measured via coordinate measuring machine (CMM) with traceability to NIST standards. Input uncertainty was propagated through the model using a Monte Carlo approach (N=1000 samples)."
