      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from production lots were tested: six at Laboratory 1 (FDA) and five at Laboratory 2 (DePuy Synthes). Inter-laboratory variability was assessed and found to be within normal manufacturing variation. Sample representativeness of the intended clinical device is confirmed."
