      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. While this configuration is the regulatory standard, it does not capture the full range of in vivo loading (e.g., torsion, lateral bending). This factor achieves only Gradation 2. This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that the COU is explicitly scoped to the F1717 compression-bending scenario.",
