      "rationale": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions, loading rate) were mapped directly to measured experimental values. Deviations between nominal and as-tested dimensions were incorporated into the simulation via measured geometry. No unresolved discrepancies in input equivalency were identified."
