      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) were compared using the ASME V&V 10 validation metric E/uval incorporating experimental uncertainty. Stiffness: 4.8% difference, E/uval=0.82. Yield force: 7.3% difference, E/uval=1.41. Force at 40 mm: 6.1% difference, E/uval=1.19. All comparisons satisfy the pre-established acceptance criteria."
