      "rationale": "The three selected QoIs are the primary metrics specified in ASTM F1717-15 and are directly linked to the clinical failure modes of interest (construct loosening, screw fracture). Stiffness characterizes immediate post-operative stability; yield force and force at 40 mm characterize fatigue-relevant structural margins. QoI relevance is rated at Gradation 3."
